description: Our mission is to serve our customers the fuel they need, so they can work hard and enjoy life to the fullest. JBirds is all about chicken (well, bacon too…for obvious and delicious reason).Chicken’s superb nutritional value cannot be understated because of its high protein content, and numerous amino acids that support the health of your bones, heart, brain & immune system. This wonderful bird has it all!  JBirds offers a variety of signature birds for you to choose from or you can (B)uild (Y)our (O)wn (B)ird. We offer the freshest ingredients to fill your bird and that's no chicken S#@%. Have a food allergy or looking for a vegetarian option? No worries...our BYOB menu has options for everyone.
name: JBirds Chicken
